									<desc xml:id="CoverFront1">the <emph rend="bold">front cover #1</emph>. Bamboo. Sticker. BnF shelfmark sticker.</desc><desc xml:id="CoverFront2">the <emph rend="bold">front cover #2</emph>.</desc><desc xml:id="U1">1 folio = <emph rend="bold">isolated stanzas</emph> (stanzas 4966-4967). Tamil foliation 14. 3 lines only on the recto. Contains a verse numbering 25. Verso blank. </desc><desc xml:id="U2">212 folios = <emph rend="bold"><term xml:lang="ta">Kamparāmāyaṇam: Āraṇiyākāṇṭam &amp; Kiṣkintakāṇṭam</term></emph>. 415 x 30 mm (but some smaller, e.g. f97 = 415 x 25 mm). Tamil foliation 1-212. Unblackened from f82 onwards.

</desc><desc xml:id="U3">133 folios = <emph rend="bold"><term xml:lang="ta">Kamparāmāyaṇam: Cuntarakāṇṭam</term></emph>. Tamil foliation 1-43, 45<hi rend="superscript">1</hi>, 45<hi rend="superscript">2</hi>, 46-133. No folio foliated 44, but the text is continuous from f43 to f45<hi rend="superscript">1</hi>.</desc><desc xml:id="U4">1 folio = <emph rend="bold"><term xml:lang="ta">Kamparāmāyaṇam: Cuntarakāṇṭam</term></emph>. Tamil foliation 1. 3 lines only on the recto. Verso blank. This appears to be a draft or duplicate of the beginning of the <term xml:lang="ta">Cuntarakāṇṭam</term>. Stanzas 1 and 2 only, with lacunae (spaces left blank). Found, at the time of examination of the bundle, between f59 and f60 of U3. Compare the text on this <locus facs="429">folio</locus> with that on <locus facs="431">U3, f1r</locus>.</desc><desc xml:id="U5">2 folios = <emph rend="bold">guard leaves</emph>. No foliation. Blank recto verso. These appear to be the front and back guard leaves, misplaced in the bundle. Foundt the time of examination of the bundle, between f59 and f60 of U3, right after U4. 
</desc><desc xml:id="CoverBack">the <emph rend="bold">back cover</emph>. Forming a set with front cover #2.</desc></collation><condition>Relatively good state of preservation, despite boreholes.</condition></supportDesc>
